stdout .

# Should report token usage on stderr
stderr 'tokens'

-- support-docs/password-reset.md --
# Password Reset

If you forgot your password, follow these steps:

1. Go to the login page
2. Click "Forgot Password"
3. Enter the email associated with your account
4. You will receive a password reset link within 5 minutes
5. Click the link and set a new password

Note: Password reset links expire after 1 hour.

-- support-docs/billing.txt --
Billing FAQ

Q: How do I update my payment method?
A: Go to Settings > Billing > Payment Methods and click "Add New".

Q: When am I billed?
A: Billing occurs on the 1st of each month.
